00:00:47.944 --> 00:00:52.502
So let me also label the
currents in these guys.

00:00:52.502 --> 00:00:55.730
This is the current in the resistor,

00:00:55.730 --> 00:00:59.147
and this is the current in the capacitor.

00:01:01.041 --> 00:01:03.730
So now I'm gonna write
the two voltage current

00:01:03.730 --> 00:01:06.119
relationships for these two components.

00:01:06.119 --> 00:01:09.869
