00:01:58.748 --> 00:02:02.748
C dv, dt, plus one over
R, times V, equals zero.

00:02:09.903 --> 00:02:12.016
Now I'm just gonna divide through by C

00:02:12.016 --> 00:02:13.349
just to be tidy.

00:02:14.292 --> 00:02:18.125
