in here, whatever it is,

00:03:07.929 --> 00:03:10.890
and then we take its derivative
and plug that in here

00:03:10.890 --> 00:03:14.593
and that has to make this
whole expression true.

00:03:14.593 --> 00:03:16.545
There's a couple of different
ways to do this, and the one

00:03:16.545 --> 00:03:18.730
