And e to the st remains.

00:04:57.366 --> 00:05:00.432
So we just took the derivative
of our proposed solution

00:05:00.432 --> 00:05:01.984
and now we're gonna plug
it into the equation

00:05:01.984 --> 00:05:03.734
and see what happens.

00:05:09.691 --> 00:05:12.762
So now I'm gonna plug in
the derivative that we had,

00:05:12.762 --> 00:05:15.178
plus the proposed solution,
