Now I'm gonna factor out,
here's the common term

00:05:47.741 --> 00:05:51.908
for each one of these, so
we'll just factor that out.

00:05:52.795 --> 00:05:56.962
So now we get ke to the st,
times S plus one over RC

00:06:06.335 --> 00:06:07.335
equals zero.

00:06:09.439 --> 00:06:12.258
Okay, now let's take
a little peek at this.

00:06:12.258 --> 00:06:14.783
We have to make this
zero by the way we pick

00:06:14.783 --> 00:06:15.616
K and S.

