00:06:22.204 --> 00:06:23.168
in the product.

00:06:23.168 --> 00:06:25.585
There's this, this, and that.

00:06:26.788 --> 00:06:29.614
Any three of these terms could be zero.

00:06:29.614 --> 00:06:32.633
The first one, K is
zero, that's a boring one

00:06:32.633 --> 00:06:35.567
