RC is the units of R times
C, ohms times farads,

00:08:14.005 --> 00:08:15.627
is actually seconds.

00:08:15.627 --> 00:08:18.764
This whole exponent has to
have no units by the time

00:08:18.764 --> 00:08:20.211
we evaluate it.

00:08:20.211 --> 00:08:23.996
And that means that RC
has to have units of time.

00:08:23.996 --> 00:08:26.921
And it's actually ohms times farads,

00:08:26.921 --> 00:08:28.921
